<br>
Guild A wants to do a raid but doesnt have anyone from essential class X online.  They look for a player X from class X. They find one that fits the bill and make that person a member.  That person takes a new job that starts at 4AM and cant come to events.<br>
<br>
Repeat above with player Y from Class X.  Player Y gets burnt out and starts playing DAOC 6 days a week.<br>
<br>
Repeat with more and more people, and what are you left with?<br>
<br>
A guild that wants to do events, but 6 nights a week cant get enough people for them and/or is missing essential classes.<br>
<br>
