<br>
I dont think Aliya's situation was handled in the proper manner, and I am sorry for that Aliya. I wish it had been handled differently.  Im sorry that the changes that we are making to make the game playable for  those who log in every night has to adversly affect you.  AV has always been a guild with goals, and raiding was and is what we plan on doing 6+ nights a week.<br>
